    to the bottom of the deck. For each of your [Mother Eater]'s digivolution cards
    in the breeding area, add 1 to this effect's play cost maximum.\n[All Turns]
    When this Digimon would leave the battle area other than by your effects, you
    may play 1 [Eater] Digimon card from your hand without paying the cost.\n[End
    of Opponent's Turn] [Once Per Turn] Delete 1 of your opponent's lowest play cost
    Digimon."
